The paper deals with a calculus for multiparty sessions enriched with security levels for messages, and proposes a monitored semantics to block the execution of processes attempting to leak information. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Logic in Computer Science (cs.LO), Cryptography and Security (cs.CR), Programming Languages (cs.PL), Software Engineering (cs.SE), and Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS) sub-categories.
